article_title: Obamacare's Double-Digit Rate Hikes For 2016 Disclosed

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: After two years of relatively stable premiums across the country, rates will jump in 2016 by double-digit percentages for individual policy purchasers on public exchanges under the Affordable Care Act in practically every state, according to the first glimpse of proposed costs for next year released by the Obama administration.
